data.description: TYBEE charmer ! This North-end Tybee beach house offers you 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, updated kitchen, Elevator, updated Roof and Windows and a huge lot to be able add an additional 1800 square feet of living space to the main floor structure and still have room to add a pool. Walking distance to North beach area, restaurants, and shopping. If you’re looking for a home on Tybee, the North side is where you want to be.
